# ============================================
# Confidential source data (PII — per Constitution Principle I)
# The SweCham Excel templates contain personal data of real members and contacts.
# They MUST NOT be committed. Keep them locally for reference only.
# ============================================
docs/*.xlsx
docs/*.xlsm
docs/*.xls
docs/~$*
# Member-import PII workbooks + generated import templates (subfolder not
# covered by the docs/*.xlsx glob above — has real member emails/TINs).
docs/import/
# Excel lock files anywhere in the repo
~$*.xls*

# Real chamber attendee CSV exports (PII per SweCham member data) —
# same rationale as the xlsx/xlsm/xls block above. Reference fixtures
# for tests live under tests/integration/events/csv-fixtures/ instead.
docs/Attendee list/
docs/Attendee\ list/

# Session-local temporary buffers (PR file lists, i18n check dumps,
# ad-hoc grep outputs) that accumulate at repo root during /code-
# review or /speckit-* workflows. Safe to delete at any time.
/pr*_files.txt
/tmp_*.txt
/tmp_*.json

# Demo seed data extracted from PII-containing workbooks (never commit).
scripts/_demo-data/
.vercel
.env*.local
.e2e-seed.json

# ============================================
# F6 perf-bench local results (R9 B.3 — orchestrator output)
# Local-environment runs are per-developer noise; only canonical
# staging baselines are committed (env-prefixed `staging-*.json`).
# ============================================
specs/012-eventcreate-integration/perf-results/local-*.json

# ============================================
# Ad-hoc verification screenshots dropped at repo root during
# Playwright-MCP / /speckit-* manual QA (e.g. f9-dashboard-admin.png).
# Root-anchored so legit assets under public/ src/ specs/ are unaffected.
# (Pre-existing tracked root PNGs are not retro-untracked by this rule.)
# ============================================
/*.png

# ============================================
# Visual-companion brainstorm mockups (superpowers)
# ============================================
.superpowers/

# Service-account credentials — never commit (present untracked at repo root)
google-credentials.json
*-credentials.json
